{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/Swift\/Dictionary\/subscript(orKey:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/Swift","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/Swift\/Dictionary"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"conformance":{"conformancePrefix":[{"type":"text","text":"Conforms when"}],"availabilityPrefix":[{"type":"text","text":"Available when"}],"constraints":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Key"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PostScriptFontNamesMapKey"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Value"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"String"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},"role":"symbol","title":"subscript(orKey:)","extendedModule":"Swift","modules":[{"name":"Foundations","relatedModules":["Swift"]}],"externalID":"s:SD15OUDSFoundationsAA25PostScriptFontNamesMapKeyVRszSSRs_rlE02orG0SSAC_tcip","roleHeading":"Instance Subscript","symbolKind":"subscript","fragments":[{"text":"subscript","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"orKey","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" _: ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Key","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"subscript"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"orKey"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"key"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Key"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"key","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The key to use to get a value"}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In fact if it seems some rules are missing, or weight are not managed, if the font family only is returned"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user has an higher probability to use the expected font. Because if a mashup of family name and weight is returned"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it can produce a PostScript identifier not available, so not usable, so implying a fallback to default system font like "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"San Francisco"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because PostScript identifiers in most of cases do not have whitespaces, remove them."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Given a dictionary with one value","    let myDict: PostScriptFontNamesMap = [PSFNMK(\"Arial\", Font.Weight.bold): \"Aria-BoldMT\"]","","    \/\/ The given value is returned if the key exists","    let keyExists = myDict[PSFNMK(\"Arial\", Font.Weight.bold)] \/\/ Arial-BoldMT","","    \/\/ But if the key does not exist, the only the key is returned","    let keyDoesNotExist = myDict[PSFNMK(\"Luciole\", Font.Weight.bold)] \/\/ Luciole"]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/swift\/dictionary\/subscript(orkey:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If there is no value for the given "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"type":"text","text":", returns the description of this key,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"i.e.font family name without the font weight in the end and without whitespaces."}],"references":{"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Contains a set of helpers and extensions shared for higher level targets."}],"images":[{"identifier":"ic_layers.png","type":"icon"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","title":"Foundations","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/Swift":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/Swift","type":"topic","title":"Swift","role":"collection","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/swift"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/Swift/Dictionary":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/Swift\/Dictionary","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/swift\/dictionary","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"extension","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SD","text":"Dictionary","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"Dictionary","abstract":[],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Dictionary","kind":"identifier"}]},"ic_layers.png":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"ic_layers.png","type":"image"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/Swift/Dictionary/subscript(orKey:)":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/Swift\/Dictionary\/subscript(orKey:)","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/swift\/dictionary\/subscript(orkey:)","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"subscript","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"orKey","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" _: ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Key","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"subscript(orKey:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If there is no value for the given "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"type":"text","text":", returns the description of this key,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"i.e.font family name without the font weight in the end and without whitespaces."}],"conformance":{"availabilityPrefix":[{"type":"text","text":"Available when"}],"conformancePrefix":[{"type":"text","text":"Conforms when"}],"constraints":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Key"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PostScriptFontNamesMapKey"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Value"},{"type":"text","text":" is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"String"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}}}}